nodes.text: Tanya Moodie is a Canadian born, British actress who portrays Bellava Parnadee in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. Other roles of note include the starring role of Hunter in Neil Gaiman's 1996 fantasy mini-series Neverwhere, Dr. Grace Sefate in Irish medical drama The Clinic, and John Watson's therapist Ella Thompson in Sherlock.
